[{"Code":"en","Title":"Activate products","Slug":"activate-products","ContentType":2,"Content":"<h3 data-block-id=\"97ce409f-6fd8-408a-9a18-6a52a8d8ed7c\">Activation methods (applicable after <a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/create-account#how-to-verify-your-business\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">account verification</a>)</h3><p data-block-id=\"fa03c8ca-aa05-47f8-b7bc-c3f20b1b8283\">Bill Payments API is still exclusively available for enterprise merchants. To activate, contact our CS team at help@xendit.co.</p><p data-block-id=\"805b2e47-8b50-4e23-a068-9dcfa63e96a7\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Activate products","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Aktifkan produk","Slug":"activate-products","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><h3 data-block-id=\"97ce409f-6fd8-408a-9a18-6a52a8d8ed7c\">Metode aktivasi (berlaku setelah <a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/create-account#how-to-verify-your-business\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">verifikasi akun</a>)</h3><p data-block-id=\"fa03c8ca-aa05-47f8-b7bc-c3f20b1b8283\">Bill Payments API hanya tersedia untuk merchant enterprise. Untuk mengaktifkan, hubungi tim CS kami di help@xendit.co.</p><p data-block-id=\"805b2e47-8b50-4e23-a068-9dcfa63e96a7\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Aktifkan produk","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"เปิดใช้งานผลิตภัณฑ์","Slug":"activate-products","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><h3 data-block-id=\"97ce409f-6fd8-408a-9a18-6a52a8d8ed7c\">วิธีการเปิดใช้งาน (ใช้ได้หลังจาก<a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/create-account#how-to-verify-your-business\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">การยืนยันบัญชี</a>)</h3><p data-block-id=\"fa03c8ca-aa05-47f8-b7bc-c3f20b1b8283\">Bill Payments API ยังคงมีให้สำหรับร้านค้าองค์กร (enterprise merchants) เท่านั้น หากต้องการเปิดใช้งาน โปรดติดต่อทีม CS ของเราที่ help@xendit.co</p><p data-block-id=\"805b2e47-8b50-4e23-a068-9dcfa63e96a7\"></p>","SeoTitle":"เปิดใช้งานผลิตภัณฑ์","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Activar productos","Slug":"activate-products","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><h3 data-block-id=\"97ce409f-6fd8-408a-9a18-6a52a8d8ed7c\">Métodos de activación (aplicables después de la <a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/create-account#how-to-verify-your-business\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">verificación de cuenta</a>)</h3><p data-block-id=\"fa03c8ca-aa05-47f8-b7bc-c3f20b1b8283\">La Bill Payments API todavía está disponible exclusivamente para comercios empresariales. Para activar, comuníquese con nuestro equipo de CS en help@xendit.co.</p><p data-block-id=\"805b2e47-8b50-4e23-a068-9dcfa63e96a7\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Activar productos","Description":null}]